## Suggested README Section: Workflow Modes

The project uses four workflow modes:

| Mode | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| Brainstorming | Explore problem space, constraints, risks, and MVP boundaries |
| Planning | Define architecture, roadmap, backlog, and implementation phases |
| Execution | Execute incrementally with tests and memory updates |
| Reflection | Review lessons, technical debt, and process improvements |

Stay in the current mode until explicitly moving to another mode.

